member.name: T:BFDR.IJEBirth
member.summary: A "wrapper" class to convert between a FHIR based BirthRecord and a record in IJE Natality format. Each property of this class corresponds exactly with a field in the IJE Natality format. The getters convert from the embedded FHIR based BirthRecord to the IJE format for a specific field, and the setters convert from IJE format for a specific field and set that value on the embedded FHIR based BirthRecord.
